- Vous aussi, monsieur.

424
00:27:46,044 --> 00:27:48,239
Keith Mars.

425
00:27:48,413 --> 00:27:50,574
J'ai un nom à faire vérifier.

426
00:27:50,749 --> 00:27:54,116
Yevgeni Sukarenko. Oui.

427
00:27:54,820 --> 00:27:57,846
- Merci, Karl.
